{
  "stem": "18102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they very quickly got me off the stool.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother put my coat back on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was September, and there was a chill in the air so she dressed me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we rushed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And another memory that I have that has plagued me to this day is the scene outside where everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The word spread like wildfire that the enemy had arrived, and everybody was running, obviously, home, as we ran.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother and I literally ran home from there to, to our residence outside of-- just outside of Bialystok's inner city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It wasn't long after that, maybe three, four hours later, that because of our location near the outskirts of Bialystok that we were the first to see the Germans arrive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a strange, eerie, frightening feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had made a, a private peek hole so that I could look out the blackened windows that my father had painted for the air raid so that I could watch.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was watching from an upstairs window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the strangest thing was that five German soldiers on horseback showed up first [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and slowly came in riding to the city.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was mesmerized by the scene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were dressed, of course, in uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "What followed were huge tanks, what looked like mammoth vehicles, at least to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were hundreds and hundreds, and they rumbled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the thing you heard first, the rumbling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So you knew something was coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then later these tanks came and, of course, it was an overwhelming feeling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was no longer any shooting or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "These were just tanks coming through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were followed-- what seemed like hundreds of tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
